## Zambia e-Visa Entry Points: Airports, Land Borders & Seaports

Know where you can enter Zambia with your e-Visa.

## Approved Entry Points

Zambia e-Visas are accepted at:

- **Kenneth Kaunda International Airport (Lusaka)**
- **Harry Mwanga Nkumbula International Airport (Livingstone)**
- **Victoria Falls Border**
- **Chirundu Border**
- **Katima Mulilo Border**

## Important Travel Tip

Specify your entry point in your application. Changing it later may not be possible.

## Can I Enter Zambia From Anywhere?

No, only use listed checkpoints.

